com.lukas783.mdt.service

Class ProcessService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lukas783.mdt.service.ProcessService

  • public class ProcessService
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton-service class that can be called statically by any class that needs to use it. Keeps a list of listeners that implement IProcessServiceListener to fire events as the service sees fit. The service is responsible for handling processing of tasks to-do.
